snippet.title: How Amber Heard Destroyed Her Own Career! (BANNED FROM HOLLYWOOD)
snippet.description:
How Amber Heard Destroyed Her Own Career! (BANNED FROM HOLLYWOOD)

Amber Heard has been the subject of several scandals following her bitter divorce from Rum Diaries co-star and popular Hollywood celebrity Johnny Depp. Johnny's fans are still cringing in the back of their minds as they watch this video. 

Amber Heard began her career slowly in 2003. However, she is now having difficulty maintaining her parts and getting cast in films.So, what was the reason for her difficulty keeping those roles? Stay tuned, and we will talk about HOW AMBER HEARD DESTROYED HER OWN CAREER.
